author: cmpilato
msg: Add a property prefix definition reserved for extra-Subversion-al
uses, and tweak a provided hook script, to encourage standardization
of how ephemeral txnprops are persisted.
* subversion/include/svn_props.h
(SVN_PROP_REVISION_PREFIX): New #define.
* tools/hook-scripts/persist-ephemeral-txnprops.py
(__doc__): Remove.
(duplicate_ephemeral_txnprops): Drop 'prefix' parameter and
handling.  Use the Python bindings' exposed "#defines" rather than
hard-coding the prefix strings we're substituting.
(usage_and_exit): Print docstring explicitly here (so we can use
string formatting/substitution).
(main): Drop 'prefix' argument handling.  Update call to
duplicate_ephemeral_txnprops().
Suggested by: danielsh
